@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About Faylz | Local File Tools</PageTitle>

<div class="bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-50 to-white pt-16 pb-12">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">About Faylz</h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Powerful file processing tools that run entirely on your device, respecting your privacy.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 border border-gray-100 mb-10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Our Mission</h2>
            <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
                <p>
                    Faylz was created with a simple mission: provide powerful file tools that respect your privacy. 
                    In an age where many "free" online tools secretly upload your files to servers, mine your data, or 
                    show intrusive ads, we wanted to create something different.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Every tool on Faylz runs 100% locally in your web browser. Your files never leave your device, 
                    ensuring complete privacy and security.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-10">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 border border-gray-100">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-full mr-4">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Privacy First</h2>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-600">
                    No servers, no data collection, no tracking. Your files stay on your device. We don't even see what files you're processing.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 border border-gray-100">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-full mr-4">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Lightning Fast</h2>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-600">
                    No waiting for uploads or downloads. Processing happens instantly on your device, making our tools much faster than cloud-based alternatives.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 border border-gray-100">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-full mr-4">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Free and Open Source</h2>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-600">
                    Our tools are completely free to use with no limitations. The code is open source, so you can verify that we do what we say.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 border border-gray-100">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-full mr-4">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Works Offline</h2>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-600">
                    After the initial load, most of our tools work completely offline. Perfect for when you're on a limited connection or traveling.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 border border-gray-100 mb-10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">How It Works</h2>
            <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
                <p>
                    Faylz leverages modern web technologies to process files directly in your browser:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <strong>WebAssembly</strong> - Allows us to run high-performance code that was previously only possible in desktop applications
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>File API</strong> - Provides secure access to files without requiring server uploads
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Web Workers</strong> - Ensures smooth performance by processing files in the background
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Blazor</strong> - Microsoft's framework for building interactive web UIs using C# instead of JavaScript
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <p>
                    All processing happens within your browser's sandbox, ensuring your files never leave your device.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 border border-blue-100">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center">
                <div class="md:w-2/3 mb-6 md:mb-0 md:pr-8">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Get Started Today</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                        Try our free tools now - no signup, no downloads, no strings attached. Just powerful file tools right in your browser.
                    </p>
                    <a href="/" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-medium px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition transform hover:-translate-y-0.5">
                        Explore Our Tools
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="md:w-1/3 flex justify-center">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-32 w-32 text-blue-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div> 